'''比利比诺核电站'''（[[俄语|俄语]]：{{lang|ru|Билибинская АЭС}}）是[[俄罗斯联邦|俄罗斯联邦]][[楚科奇自治区|楚科奇自治区]][[比利比诺|比利比诺]]的一座电站，安装四台EGP-6型[[核反应堆|核反应堆]]，装机容量48MW，是世界上最小的核电站，也是北半球纬度最高的核电站<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=Swr9BTI_2FEC&pg=PA241|publisher=[[劳特里奇|Routledge]]|date=2005-09-23|isbn=978-1-136-78680-8|language=en|first=Mark|last=Nuttall|title=Encyclopedia of the Arctic|pages=241|access-date=2019-06-09|archive-date=2021-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003092059/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=Swr9BTI_2FEC&pg=PA241|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當局宣佈計劃在2019年啟動關閉該核電站的程-{}-序<ref>{{Cite web|title=Билибинская АЭС на Чукотке будет остановлена в 2019 году|url=https://regnum.ru/news/economy/2103335.html|access-date=2021-10-03|date=2016-03-23|work=ИА REGNUM|language=ru|archive-date=2021-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003092032/https://regnum.ru/news/economy/2103335.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，將由[[羅蒙諾索夫院士浮動核能發電廠|羅蒙諾索夫院士浮動核能發電廠]]取代<ref name="wnn-20161007">{{cite news|url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/WR-Work-starts-on-on-shore-infrastructure-for-Russian-floating-plant-0710165.html|title=Work starts on on-shore infrastructure for Russian floating plant|publisher=World Nuclear News|date=7 October 2016|accessdate=12 October 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609173718/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/WR-Work-starts-on-on-shore-infrastructure-for-Russian-floating-plant-0710165.html|archive-date=2019-06-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

